    • org.microemu.cldc.file.FileSystem (implements org.microemu.microedition.ImplementationInitialization)
    • org.microemu.cldc.file.FileSystemFileConnection (implements javax.microedition.io.file.FileConnection)
    • javax.microedition.io.file.FileSystemRegistry
    • org.microemu.cldc.file.FileSystemRegistryImpl (implements org.microemu.cldc.file.FileSystemRegistryDelegate, org.microemu.microedition.Implementation)
    • org.microemu.cldc.file.InMemory (implements org.microemu.microedition.ImplementationInitialization)
    • java.lang.Throwable (implements java.io.Serializable)
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • javax.microedition.io.file.ConnectionClosedException
          • javax.microedition.io.file.IllegalModeException
